    <p>• Launch the lat­est ver­sion of the DBS di­gibank app. • Select the iden­tity type: NRIC, Malaysian IC or</p>
    <p>pass­port.</p>
    <p>• En­ter the iden­tity num­ber.</p>
    <p>• Select SingPass Face Ver­i­fi­ca­tion to ver­ify the user. • Take the selfie.</p>
    <p>• The cap­tured im­age will be matched in­stantly against the lat­est records in the Gov­ern­ment’s bio­met­ric data­base.</p>
    <p>• Upon suc­cess­ful match­ing, DBS will send a one-time pass­word (OTP) to the user’s reg­is­tered mo­bile num­ber via SMS.</p>
    <p>• En­ter the OTP and create a user ID to reg­is­ter an</p>
    <p>on­line ac­count to ac­cess mo­bile bank­ing ser­vices. • The fa­cial data will not be re­tained by the bank.</p>


